p: The chemotype A (from São Paulo state samples) is characterized by the presence of isospathulenol (peak 39), α-bisabolol (peak 42), β-bisabolene (peak 22) and ( E)-nerolidol (peak 46), while the chemotype B (from Mato Grosso do Sul state samples) by the compounds bicyclogermacrene (peak 13) and elemicin (peak 48).
